---
description: Temporal workers, workflows bundle, and global types.
globs: apps/temporal/**
---

### Workers and bundles

- Base workers: `analyzer`, `dispatcher`, `fetcher`. Source `workflows/<base>.ts` → bundle `dist/workflows/<base>.js` (see [build.workflows.ts](apps/temporal/build.workflows.ts)).
- New child workflows: align with `WorkflowType` and existing `workflows/*.ts` / activity modules.

### Types

- New activity groups or contract changes: update [types/global.d.ts](apps/temporal/types/global.d.ts) (`*Activities`, `TaskQueue`, etc.) so `proxyActivities` and tests stay typed.
